@@TJvDirectorySpy
Description:
This component allows you to spy a directory and his subdirectories. You can spy FileName changes, directory name changes, attriJvtes changes, size changes, last write changes (and secturiy changes under windows NT). <COLOR Red>Be aware, using a security spy under windows 95/98 will fail !</COLOR>.

